    <summary>AI-powered Windows optimization and maintenance platform.</summary>
    <description>
NeoOptimize is a local Windows utility for diagnostics, safe cleanup, repair planning, update checks, NEO Agentic Autopilot, and before/after maintenance reports.

Maintenance actions are designed to be visible and user-approved. Administrator approval may be required for privileged Windows repair operations.
    </description>
